{"tid":1632211,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)鬼滅之刃","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T14:31:21.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e0542aa20c8bd5b72f5818d6b15fbb6524bf4252","tid":1632211,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:15:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啊~~~死黑警~~~又唔做嘢又唔讀書</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=17433abe\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=817c7727\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=ec476cba\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/bangumi/edbdecd451315bc573ed22009f68efdd4ab91bed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.hdslb.com%2Fbfs%2Fbangumi%2Fedbdecd451315bc573ed22009f68efdd4ab91bed.png&h=7df6abb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《鬼滅之刃》（日語：鬼滅の刃）是由日本漫畫家吾峠呼世晴所創作的日本漫畫作品，於《週刊少年Jump》2016年11號開始連載中。以大正時代為故事舞台，講述了主角竈門炭治郎全家被鬼殺害，為了尋求唯一倖存但被鬼化的妹妹變回人的方法，踏上了斬鬼之旅所描寫的純和風劍戟奇譚<br />\n<br />\n 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=f29277b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=44ab0d0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af89d88a6e5637a0f2793f64ee1aec23e0ba7d5b","tid":1632211,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d735ee7829d073a01a8dafc5008fb6d1b9c1e0","tid":1632211,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810872cafef7967538fd512df8b0312fb3d6081f","tid":1632211,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d058c01164465a452eb70c24f74f09b4bb2723